tableCalculations.name: average_daily_num_releases_per_engineer_rolling_7d_average_excluding_weekends__1
tableCalculations.displayName: average daily num releases per engineer (rolling 7d average excluding weekends)
tableCalculations.sql: ROUND(SUM(${github_daily.releases_published_num}) OVER(PARTITION BY NULL ORDER BY ${github_daily.date_day}  ASC ROWS BETWEEN 6 PRECEDING AND CURRENT ROW) / 6 / 5, 1)
